{"tid":962647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中金料中石化庫存減值150億人幣","createTime":"2018-12-31T04:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T06:18:31.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"49cdb2d4fcab236689a834236fb64cbd17fe10af","tid":962647,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T04:41:23.000Z","msg":"中金料中石化庫存減值150億人幣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2025366/%E4%B8%AD%E9%87%91%E6%96%99%E4%B8%AD%E7%9F%B3%E5%8C%96%E5%BA%AB%E5%AD%98%E6%B8%9B%E5%80%BC150%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2025366%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%259F%25B3%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%25BA%25AB%25E5%25AD%2598%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%2580%25BC150%25E5%2584%2584%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B9%25A3&d=fCOYiJelhX8M7wCogUqPFv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=f6122a6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2025366/%E4%B8%AD%E9%87%91%E6%96%99%E4%B8%AD%E7%9F%B3%E5%8C%96%E5%BA%AB%E5%AD%98%E6%B8%9B%E5%80%BC150%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%A3</a><br />\n<br />\n中石化(00386)昨日發表公告，證實旗下聯合石化在某些原油交易過程中，因油價下跌產生部分損失，兩名負責人因工作原因停職。據券商中金估計，中石化近期的庫存減值金額高達150億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n中金最新研究報告指出，除了聯合石化的交易虧損外，原油價格於今年第四季跌幅超過20美元，亦令中石化面臨龐大的庫存減值。該行估計，中石化於今年10月至明年1月期間，將有大約150億元人民幣的庫存損失入賬，導致業績雪上加霜。<br />\n<br />\n花旗指出，假設聯合石化虧損金額10億美元，則中石化2018年度盈利將會減少7%。摩根士丹利則認為，中石化需要採取行動重建投資者信心。"},{"pid":"1634e610625b6d7cf7e218b60bbc3fb636b80889","tid":962647,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5777f44d98fcde9250c66bd052ae6b18b250e59e","tid":962647,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:18:31.000Z","msg":"之前新聞都有講佢地都唔鍊油, 直接同新加坡買油, 係新加坡只係個幾入貨, 佢係支那賣6個幾, 扣埋成本基本淨賺50%以上, 咁都仲要去炒期油<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}